name: Gobluild
skill: Restore 3718/4578 HP to self, increase crit rate for a limited time 20%
ability: Slightly increases max HP of all allies.

additional_data.description: The spirit of a brave goblin with a strong sense of justice. A heroine among goblins, she worships the goblin gods of old and overcame great obstacles in order to obtain their ancient wisdom. No other goblins remember the old gods like she does—only she still knows their true names. These gods had the pwoer to destroy the balance of the world, and so they altered goblins' memories to prevent their religion from spreading. That was the first time she resisted the gods' wishes. She refuses to forget how they sacrificed themselves for the greater good.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Limited Jewel Summon from 30/08/2017 - 06/09/2017
◦ Trade at Exchange for 50 Mochi 06/09/2017
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Summon rate increased until 06/09/2017
◦ Can only be exchanged once

summon: "My name's Gobild, and I'm a goblin! Nice to meet you!"
